  "Negotiator": {
    "skills": ["Negotiation", "Culture", "Insight"],
    "flavor": """
      <p>In a world of broken treaties and shattered alliances, the Negotiator is the glue that holds civilization together. They understand that every conflict has a solution that leaves both parties feeling like they won, and every person has needs that can be met without violence.</p>
      <p>Negotiators are masters of diplomacy and cultural understanding, able to bridge gaps between factions that have been at war for generations. They know that the most important battle is the one that never happens, and the most valuable resource is mutual understanding.</p>
    """,
    "perk": "Diplomatic Immunity",
    "techniques": [
      "Keep Your Cool",
      "Read the Room",
      "Concession",
      "Everyone Has a Price",
      "Manners maketh the Man",
      "Negotiation Tactics",
      "Operational Insight",
      "Strategic Insight",
      "Tactical Assessment",
      "Two Heads are Better than One",
      "Bond of Heroes",
      "Flexible Positioning"
    ],
    "capstone": "Master Diplomat"
  },

  "Commander": {
    "skills": ["Command", "Tactics", "Resolve"],
    "flavor": """
      <p>A Commander creates certainty in chaos. When bullets fly and systems fail, they are the calm voice that guides the team through hell and back.</p>
      <p>Commanders are masters of leadership and battlefield strategy, able to turn a group of individuals into a cohesive unit that moves and fights as one. They understand that morale is as important as ammunition, and that the right word at the right time can be more powerful than any weapon.</p>
    """,
    "perk": "Natural Leader",
