  "Netrunner": {
    "skills": ["Computers", "Subterfuge", "Insight"],
    "flavor": """
      <p>In the digital shadows of 2072, a Netrunner is both ghost and god. They slip through firewalls like smoke and leave no trace of their passing. The Netrunner wages war in the silent spaces between signals.</p>
      <p>Netrunners are experts in electronic warfare, able to infiltrate secure networks and turn enemy systems against their owners. In 2072, a well-placed line of code is the most dangerous weapon in existence.</p>
    """,
    "perk": "Ghost in the Machine",
    "techniques": [
      "Blackout",
