  "Analyst": {
    "skills": ["Science", "Insight", "Medicine"],
    "flavor": """
      <p>Every problem has an answer, if you know where to look. The Analyst is the operator who reads what others overlook, connecting scattered data points into a coherent picture while everyone else is still asking questions.</p>
      <p>Analysts combine scientific expertise with sharp observational instincts, serving as the intellectual backbone of any team. When the mission depends on understanding what happened and why, the Analyst is the one who figures it out.</p>
    """,
    "perk": "Analytical Mind",
